Package com.hazelcast.core

Interface DistributedObjectListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener
    public interface DistributedObjectListener
extends EventListener
    DistributedObjectListener notifies when a DistributedObject is created or destroyed cluster-wide.
    See Also:
    DistributedObject, HazelcastInstance.addDistributedObjectListener(DistributedObjectListener)
